# =============================================================================
# Per-Space Fingerprint Resistance — Detailed Patch Guide
# =============================================================================
#
# This document describes the exact modifications needed to make Firefox's
# fingerprint resistance (RFP) work per-container instead of globally.
#
# In vanilla Firefox, `privacy.resistFingerprinting` is a single boolean pref.
# When enabled, it applies the SAME fingerprint spoofing to ALL tabs. This is
# fine for privacy, but useless for anti-detect because every tab looks identical.
#
# SpaceBrowser needs each Space (container) to have its OWN fingerprint profile:
# different canvas noise, different WebGL values, different navigator properties.
#
# This patch modifies 7 core Firefox source files to achieve this.
#
# =============================================================================

