# =============================================================================
# INTEGRATION FLOW SUMMARY
# =============================================================================
#
# The data flow for per-space fingerprinting:
#
# 1. User creates a Space in the UI
#    → SpaceIdentityService.create() in JS
#    → Generates fingerprint profile (deterministic from UUID)
#    → Stores in spaces.json
#
# 2. Space profile is pushed to C++ layer
#    → RFPHelper.sys.mjs bridges JS → C++
#    → Calls nsRFPService::RegisterSpaceProfile()
#    → Profile cached in sSpaceProfiles map
#
# 3. Tab opens in a Space container
#    → Tab's OriginAttributes.mUserContextId = space's userContextId
#    → All code in that tab inherits these attributes
#
# 4. Fingerprinting-sensitive code runs
#    → Canvas getImageData() called
#    → Checks OriginAttributes → finds userContextId
#    → Looks up SpaceFingerprintProfile
#    → Applies per-space noise instead of global RFP
#
# 5. HTTP requests go out
#    → nsHttpChannel gets loadInfo with OriginAttributes
#    → Looks up per-space User-Agent
#    → Sends space-specific headers
#
# This ensures complete isolation: each Space has its own fingerprint
# across ALL vectors (canvas, WebGL, audio, navigator, UA, screen).
# =============================================================================
